{"tid":2408901,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"作為同樣怨恨世界冷眼旁觀嘅香港人，我哋應該更大力支持緬甸","createTime":"2021-02-15T10:48:12.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-19T16:02:53.000Z","uid":358892,"like":23,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"7cd014544c2301990dfd88bdd71904cd473c46b1","tid":2408901,"uid":358892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T10:48:12.000Z","msg":"唔知係剩係我個圈子<br />\n定還是大家都係咁<br />\n發現今次緬甸單嘢<br />\n唔再見到香港人熱心retweet<br />\n相信香港人呢兩年來受盡中共港共政權嘅各種壓迫嘅時候<br />\n見到外國人唔理、特別嗰啲咩「世界XX組織」齋講唔做、啲荷里活NBA人權鬥士扮睇唔到，都覺得好怨憤<br />\n正所謂「己所不欲，勿施於人」<br />\n我諗大家都唔想成為自己最怨恨嘅嗰班外國bystanders<br />\n特別今次緬甸單嘢<br />\n9成背後又係有中共搞鬼<br />\n所以，雖然知道香港人自己都好辛苦<br />\n但都盡量出力<br />\n聲援緬甸<br />\n<br />\n#WhatsHappeningInMyanmar<br />\n#Feb14Coup<br />\n#Feb15Coup<br />\n#SaveMyanmar<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/frontiermm/status/1361228502582747140?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Ffrontiermm%2Fstatus%2F1361228502582747140%3Fs%3D21&d=lQL0ZJWU6LWL4dZDafr4eZKGII16X6EVRppoT8yKAsg%3D&h=b591d303\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Ffrontiermm%2Fstatus%2F1361228502582747140%3Fs%3D21&h=1ddefa84\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/frontiermm/status/1361228502582747140?s=21</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/mrs_pp28/status/1361161914152153089?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fmrs_pp28%2Fstatus%2F1361161914152153089%3Fs%3D21&d=lQL0ZJWU6LWL4dZDafr4eZKGII16X6EVRppoT8yKAsg%3D&h=6b154137\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fmrs_pp28%2Fstatus%2F1361161914152153089%3Fs%3D21&h=038606f9\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/mrs_pp28/status/1361161914152153089?s=21</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/hannayuri_twt/status/1360995640726089736?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhannayuri_twt%2Fstatus%2F1360995640726089736%3Fs%3D21&d=lQL0ZJWU6LWL4dZDafr4eZKGII16X6EVRppoT8yKAsg%3D&h=b8e0ada0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhannayuri_twt%2Fstatus%2F1360995640726089736%3Fs%3D21&h=334b0442\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/hannayuri_twt/status/1360995640726089736?s=21</a><br />\n<br />\n[有片，全部入嚟RT] 緬甸軍方向平民開鎗<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2408347/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2408347/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n「天佑緬甸」緬甸軍方已頒布黨安法 違法者將判監20年<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2408499/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2408499/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n緬甸斷網期間 有三架不知名飛機於緬甸仰光與中國昆明來回<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2408367/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2408367/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"a8340a07647e5b84e773f096d92844209906fef2","tid":2408901,"uid":62259,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T10:49:54.000Z","msg":"香港人要返工 不了"},{"pid":"f74bab299f9d4c36eaf5d944dd48c72fb36e2c09","tid":2408901,"uid":140924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T10:51:33.000Z","msg":"我諗只係好多人都無再玩Twitter <br />\n但有見過部分手足嘅身影<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b3cede7167b2b330946a89a19017b0b17da20cc","tid":2408901,"uid":128369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T10:54:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d04b0758d995b173388400ff182a326418a2bc5","tid":2408901,"uid":308251,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T10:57:33.000Z","msg":"出聲點解要用twitter, 我屌你老母啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不如用埋微博啦柒咕碌<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/yea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"128d